HEADWORD: Sperm
<hw>Sperm</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos><ety>[F. <ets>sperme</ets>, L.
<ets>sperma</ets>, Gr. <?/<?/<?/, <?/<?/<?/, from <?/<?/<?/<?/ to sow.
Cf. <er>Spore</er>.]</ety> <fld>(Physiol.)</fld> <def>The male
fecundating fluid; semen. See <er>Semen</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
