==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Sperm
<hw>Sperm</hw>, <pos>n.</pos><ety>[Contr. fr.
<ets>spermaceti</ets>.]</ety> <def>Spermaceti.</def>⟦br⟧
